<p style="text-indent: 2.125em;">习近平总书记在2024年全国教育大会上强调，紧紧围绕立德树人根本任务，朝着建成教育强国战略目标扎实迈进。江西教育系统牢记嘱托，砥砺奋进，奋力书写教育强省建设支撑引领中国式现代化江西篇章。即日起，江西省教育厅微信公众号推出<span style="color: rgb(231, 0, 37);"><strong>“奋进在教育强省大路上”</strong></span>专栏，全面展示我省教育系统实施科教强省战略的生动实践和广大教师立德树人、自信自强的精神风貌。</p><p style="text-indent: 2.125em;">今天推出<strong>“职业教育篇”</strong>，通过一组大图、一篇报道、一组数据介绍江西如何扎实推进职业教育高质量发展——</p><p style="text-indent: 2.125em;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1747571961166.png" alt="1747571961166.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1747571961166.png" style="width: 100%;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1747571975732.png" alt="1747571975732.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1747571975732.png" style="width: 100%;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1747571992557.png" alt="1747571992557.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1747571992557.png" style="width: 100%;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1747572003330.png" alt="1747572003330.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1747572003330.png" style="width: 100%;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1747572015118.png" alt="1747572015118.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1747572015118.png" style="width: 100%;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1747572025986.png" alt="1747572025986.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1747572025986.png" style="width: 100%;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1747572035436.png" alt="1747572035436.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1747572035436.png" style="width: 100%;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1747572048560.png" alt="1747572048560.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1747572048560.png" style="width: 100%;"></p>